data.description: Craftsman home with a 32ft x 26ft stall garage. This home has been totally redone, including new insulation, wiring, 5/8 high efficiency windows, siding, soffit and doors. Updated kitchen along with newer laminate floors and carpet. Natural gas forced air furnace. Dual Sanyo heat pump unit provides air conditioning. 26' X 32' detached garage was added to the rear of the property with nice driveway. This home has the charm of old, but has the advantage of new, property for sale at 320 15th St N, Moorhead, MN, USA. This single-family, 1 1/2 story, has 3 bedrooms, 1 bathroom and approximately 1,260 sqft of floor space. This property was built in 1900.
